channel.title: Blank Source And Client | Delta
channel.description:
My first Upload
im beginner at coding.
The Blank Source Is A 317 Delta Scape. The Blank Client Is A 317 Delta Client. ;D Basic Blank Source Very Very Easy To Code!
There is char called Im username im password: nothing(dont type anything just log in) Find A Line That Says Player Rights: Change The Following: "Character-Rights = 0" Change The "0" To Which Ever Of The Following You Want: Normal Player: "0" Moderator: "1" Administrator: "2" Owner/Co-Owner: "3" Hidden Administrator: "4" Donator: "5" To Change Donator Another Way Find A Line In The .Txt Files Called: "Character-isMember: "0" Change The "0" To "1"
Downloads: Source And Client Package [url=http://www.dropbox.com/s/tg34yvpwyf5ikda/Blank.zip]www.dropbox.com/s/tg34yvpwyf5ikda/Blank.zip[/url]
